<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="339" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="24.[835,1475,315,431]" pageId="24" pageNumber="339">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[835,1278,315,339]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="339">Distribution and seasonal occurrence. –</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[1286,1384,315,338]" name="Thailand" pageId="24" pageNumber="339">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. Known from one locality only. Records are from the first decade of February to late May. Collected on riverbanks in gallery forest.
</paragraph>
